thread.title: Several Killed as Truck Rams Into Small Crowd in Münster, Germany - WSJ

author: Bojan Pancevski
title: Several Killed as Truck Rams Into Small Crowd in Münster, Germany - WSJ
text:
BERLIN—At least two people were killed and six were seriously injured after a man drove a van into a group of people in the center of the western German city of Münster on Saturday, police said.
The suspected driver also shot himself dead after ramming the vehicle into a huddle of people sitting in front of the Grosser Kiepenkerl, a landmark restaurant in the historic center of the city, a police spokesman said.
